# Architecture

- Scenes: Phaser lifecycle only (create/update/shutdown) — no game logic
- All game logic in src/managers/ classes
- Scene-to-scene communication via `this.game.events` emitter only
- HUDScene runs parallel to GameScene via `scene.launch()`, reacts to events only
- Single `gameState` object on `this.game`, passed by reference to all managers
- Player.js handles sprite, physics, jump — never score or spawn logic
- All textures generated procedurally in BootScene — no external image assets
